WHY AGPL-3.0-OR-LATER

The Remnant is distributed bundled with SillyTavern, which is licensed
under the GNU Affero General Public License version 3 or later. Because
The Remnant's extension code is loaded into SillyTavern's runtime and
because the project redistributes SillyTavern inside its Docker images,
the combined work is a derivative that must be offered under AGPL-3.0
or a compatible copyleft license. We choose AGPL-3.0-or-later
deliberately rather than reluctantly — see NOTICES.md for the full
reasoning and the project's position on commercial use.

See NOTICES.md for attributions and licenses of all third-party
components, model weights, and assets used by this project.
